<br>
As in add the extra 3hp/tick you have sitting to your manna pool when you're at full HP?<br>
<br>
This would allow pre Level 56 Magicians faster manna regen (since once we get Mystical Transvergence, most mages have one summoned to utilise our phantom armour spells more efficiently)<br>
<br>
Although this wouldn't be in effect when the magician had been damaged, it would help when we're sitting on our asses waiting for the HP to regen.<br>
<br>
I don't think it woudl be a good idea to allow all HP regen to translate to manna regen (since you can regen horrendus amounts with druid/shaman spells) but the plain old baseline amount. (this may be an issue with iksar)<br>
<br>
NBV. This shouldn't detract from the suefulness of Transvergence as a manna regen tool, depending on hiw fast you regen your manna.<br>
<br>
Questions? Commnts? Constructive criticisms? <p>Majishia Vie <Wyrd Angles>
